            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1239495</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">PlayStation 於其官方節目「State of Play」中宣佈《戰神：諸神黃昏》（God of War Ragnarök）將會於 9 月 19 日登陸 PC 平台，但需要使用 PSN（PlayStation Network）的帳號登入後才能遊玩。目前已於 Steam 和 Epic Game Store 開放預購，並會要求連結至 PSN 帳號。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1239506" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/53758742049_986a0ed3-694x390.jpg" alt="God of War Ragnarök" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/53758742049_986a0ed3-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/53758742049_986a0ed3.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://blog.playstation.com/2024/05/30/god-of-war-ragnarok-is-coming-to-pc/">PlayStation.Blog</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">《戰神：諸神黃昏》PC 版將支援 4K 解析度，整合 NVIDIA RTX 深度學習超高採樣（DLSS）技術、AMD FidelityFX 超級解析度（FSR），以及 Intel XeSS（Xe 超高採樣）等，無上限幀率而且支援 21:9 和 32:9 的超寛螢幕模式。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1239504" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/53758825510_ed8d58a6-694x390.jpg" alt="God of War Ragnarök" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/53758825510_ed8d58a6-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/53758825510_ed8d58a6.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://blog.playstation.com/2024/05/30/god-of-war-ragnarok-is-coming-to-pc/">PlayStation.Blog</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">目前於 9 月 19 日前預購《戰神：諸神黃昏》，可以得到克雷多斯甦雪盔甲、阿特柔斯甦雪束腰上衣（外觀）的預購特典，兩者均可在推進遊戲劇情期間獲得。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1239505" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/53758825500_1ec2a8b4-694x390.jpg" alt="God of War Ragnarök" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/53758825500_1ec2a8b4-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/53758825500_1ec2a8b4.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://blog.playstation.com/2024/05/30/god-of-war-ragnarok-is-coming-to-pc/">PlayStation.Blog</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">預購亦有推出豪華版，收錄克雷多斯黑谷盔甲、阿特柔斯黑谷服裝（外觀）、混沌雙刀用黑谷雙刀手柄、利維坦之斧用黑谷斧柄、官方《戰神：諸神黃昏》數位原聲帶和 Dark Horse 迷你數位美術集。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源：<a href="https://blog.playstation.com/2024/05/30/god-of-war-ragnarok-is-coming-to-pc/">PlayStation.Blog</a></p><p>圖片來源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=m-4ZM3jxhdE&amp;t=763s">PlayStation</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/27/%e3%80%90%e8%a9%95%e6%b8%ac%e3%80%91ps5%e3%80%8a%e6%b5%aa%e4%ba%ba%e5%b4%9b%e8%b5%b7%e3%80%8b%e3%80%80%e5%b9%95%e6%9c%ab%e4%ba%82%e4%b8%96%e6%b4%bb%e5%87%ba%e8%87%aa%e7%94%b1/game-channel/game-review/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【評測】PS5《浪人崛起》　幕末亂世活出自由</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/31/monsterhunterwilds/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Monster Hunter Wilds 首段預告片【有片睇】新魔物 + 新坐騎 + 新玩法</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/28/chinaminors-refundstandard/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">中國首個未成年遊戲退款標準發布，未成年人不受限充值遊戲公司需負責</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/31/gow5-on-pc/game-channel/">《戰神：諸神黃昏》9 月登陸 PC　需要用 PSN 帳號登入才可玩</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
