                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">魔物獵人系列繼《Monster Hunter World》和《Monster Hunter Rise》後，上年年尾公佈最新作品《Monster Hunter Wilds》。今日 Capcom 在 PlayStation 官方節目「State of Play」中正式公開首段預告片，片中出現的遊玩片段除了展示多款新魔物，還公開了新的能力和坐騎等新玩法。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_63378"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/BTCFmHCsqM0?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1239462" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/53758797114_094a2076-1-694x390.jpg" alt="Monster Hunter Wilds" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/53758797114_094a2076-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/53758797114_094a2076-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1239463" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/53757557667_e2137301-694x390.jpg" alt="Monster Hunter Wilds" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/53757557667_e2137301-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/53757557667_e2137301.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://blog.playstation.com/2024/05/30/monster-hunter-wilds-new-gameplay-details-from-todays-state-of-play/">PlayStation.Blog</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">本次新添加的地形「迎風平原」（Windward Plains）會不斷變化，同時存在沙漠、草原和巖層，不同的地形環境和天氣都象徵着不同的狩獵挑戰。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1239464" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/53758796954_06f4e1ea-694x390.jpg" alt="Monster Hunter Wilds" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/53758796954_06f4e1ea-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/53758796954_06f4e1ea.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://blog.playstation.com/2024/05/30/monster-hunter-wilds-new-gameplay-details-from-todays-state-of-play/">PlayStation.Blog</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">新登場「Seikret」是於此處穿梭的必備坐騎，小巧並有靈敏的嗅覺能力，於移動中可以補充戰力，而且不返回基地便可以切換主副武器。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1239466" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/go3ipuca4am1tt-694x390.jpg" alt="Monster Hunter Wilds" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/go3ipuca4am1tt-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/go3ipuca4am1tt.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1239468" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/53758666313_c6c08d6f-694x390.jpg" alt="Monster Hunter Wilds" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/53758666313_c6c08d6f-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/53758666313_c6c08d6f.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1239467" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/go3i2oxaiaaywwp-694x390.jpg" alt="Monster Hunter Wilds" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/go3i2oxaiaaywwp-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/go3i2oxaiaaywwp.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://blog.playstation.com/2024/05/30/monster-hunter-wilds-new-gameplay-details-from-todays-state-of-play/">PlayStation.Blog</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">新登場的魔物包括具巨型獠牙的牙獸種「Doshaguma」，利用背部類似避雷針的角來保護族羣抵受風沙侵襲的草食種「Ceratonoth」，擁有巨大舌頭及滑稽唾液的兩生種「Chatacabra」。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1239465" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/53758879255_9d03e4e4-694x390.jpg" alt="Monster Hunter Wilds" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/53758879255_9d03e4e4-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/53758879255_9d03e4e4.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://blog.playstation.com/2024/05/30/monster-hunter-wilds-new-gameplay-details-from-todays-state-of-play/">PlayStation.Blog</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">增添的新能力「專注模式」（Focus Mode）發動時能更精準的防禦、瞄準和攻擊。預告中亦確認了前作的 14 種武器全數回歸，並追加了新的動作。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1239458 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire-1717133965-scaled-e1717134006439-694x388.jpg" alt="Monster Hunter Wilds" width="694" height="388" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire-1717133965-scaled-e1717134006439-694x388.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire-1717133965-scaled-e1717134006439-1280x717.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BTCFmHCsqM0">capcomasia</a></p><p>《Monster Hunter Wilds》承繼《Monster Hunter World》的開放式世界玩法，所以為了回饋《Monster Hunter World》和 《Monster Hunter World: Iceborne》的玩家，只要持有上述兩隻遊戲的存檔便可以獲得對應的防具和武器特典。遊戲會於 2025 年推出，登陸 PS5、Xbox 和 PC 平台。預測 6 月 7 日的 Summer Game Fest 將公開更多遊戲資訊。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源：<a href="https://www.4gamers.com.tw/news/detail/64936/monster-hunter-wilds-first-trailer-is-here-state-of-play?fbclid=IwZXh0bgNhZW0CMTAAAR2OC-r7qv9yAjXtFJXDrQeyro5S0ZpEIpR9VkeHxr4eM7oUVAWcA9w0FK4_aem_AcdPViL7RkpwqULuOhnsD7mwI_vzb5mvUDH07m8myE4o7UbynYyir_hk3fW8WwAiJdEuiZbuWtzZgfBSTQ3-ePIF">4Gamers</a>、<a href="https://www.ign.com/articles/monster-hunter-wilds-new-trailer-new-monsters-2024">IGN</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">圖片來源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=O3syM4tV8Xw">The Game Awards</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/27/%e3%80%90%e8%a9%95%e6%b8%ac%e3%80%91ps5%e3%80%8a%e6%b5%aa%e4%ba%ba%e5%b4%9b%e8%b5%b7%e3%80%8b%e3%80%80%e5%b9%95%e6%9c%ab%e4%ba%82%e4%b8%96%e6%b4%bb%e5%87%ba%e8%87%aa%e7%94%b1/game-channel/game-review/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【評測】PS5《浪人崛起》　幕末亂世活出自由</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/31/gow5-on-pc/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">《戰神：諸神黃昏》9 月登陸 PC　需要用 PSN 帳號登入才可玩</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/28/chinaminors-refundstandard/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">中國首個未成年遊戲退款標準發布，未成年人不受限充值遊戲公司需負責</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/31/monsterhunterwilds/game-channel/">Monster Hunter Wilds 首段預告片【有片睇】新魔物 + 新坐騎 + 新玩法</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
